                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-17-off106 t18301028-17-cd107"></join>, 6 handkerchiefs, value 20s.; 50 yards of printed cotton, value 40s.; 12 yards of linen, value 16s.; 40 yards of lace, value 30s.; 4 yards of cambric, value 4s.; 3 shawls, value 30s., and 1 packing-case, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
